==English==
===Transitive Verb===
'''to relinquish'''
# to [[give up]], [[abandon]] or [[retire]] from something
# to [[stop]] doing something; or not to start on an intended action
# to let go, either physically ([[release]]) or metaphorically ([[surrender]])

